elements_min.selector_pref: [aria-label="Whimsical children’s storybook illustration—crafted in mixed media with expressive inky brushstrokes, delicate bleach splatters, and thick swirls of oil paint overlays. Perched confidently on the horse’s back, a fluffy, oversized black cat with enormous, glowing yellow eyes grins mischievously, its fur rendered in wild, inky strokes. Beside them, a vibrantly coral-hued bird, small and luminous, darts through the air, trailing sparks of color. The moon hangs as a slender, silver crescent among wispy clouds, casting soft glimmers over a shadowy field where abstract, jet-black wildflowers bloom—each petal textured with ink and subtle orange gradients, echoing the night’s magical embrace. The entire scene is suffused with a storybook charm; each detail invites curiosity and wonder. — Tiberiu Prunes"]
